<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_2289572acfe0.aspx"><b>国风·郑风·山有扶苏</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson2289572acfe0">
<p>山有扶苏，隰有荷华。不见子都，乃见狂且。<br />山有乔松，隰有游龙，不见子充，乃见狡童。</p>
</div>
</div>
