<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_7bc2f37acf1e.aspx"><b>国风·召南·野有死麕</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson7bc2f37acf1e">
野有死麕，白茅包之。有女怀春，吉士诱之。<br />林有朴樕，野有死鹿。白茅纯束，有女如玉。<br />舒而脱脱兮！无感我帨兮！无使尨也吠！
</div>
